headline: UDR to Participate in 2025 Citi Global Property CEO Conference
summary: DENVER, February 27, 2025--UDR, Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: UDR), a leading multifamily real estate investment trust, announced today that Thomas W. Toomey, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, and the UDR Executive Team will host a roundtable discussion at the 2025 Citi Global Property CEO Conference in Hollywood, Florida, on Tuesday, March 4, 2025, at 11:40 a.m. Eastern Time.
